CVS: ----------------------------------------------------------------------
CVS: CMake commit messages must be formatted as follows:
CVS:
CVS:   - The first line must have at least 8 characters.
CVS:   - The first line must not have leading whitespace.
CVS:   - The second line, if any, must be empty.
CVS:
CVS: (We no longer require prefixes like "ENH:", "BUG:", etc.)
CVS: ----------------------------------------------------------------------
